},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract